You can use this as standalone middleware with app.use(helmet.crossOriginEmbedderPolicy()).Cross-Origin-Opener-PolicyDefault:Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin
The Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy header helps process-isolate your page. For more, see MDN’s article on this header.// Sets "Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin"
